from IPython.display import Image, Markdown, display

# Funktion zur Darstellung eines Blocks mit Bild und Beschreibung
def display_block(title, description, image_path, image_width=794, image_height=300):
    display(Markdown(f"""
    ### **{title}**
    {description}
    """))
    display(Image(filename=image_path, width=image_width, height=image_height))
